        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 99e20011-f68b-47a0-bf4a-b2ceb63ebde0).Image",
        "Description": "Two bartenders in Berlin have been giving away secrets to an unknown source on how to get into the club.\r\rYour job is to seek out these bartenders and eliminate them in a way that you won’t be noticed. Maybe give them a taste of what they&apos;re serving.\r \rAlso do not harm any of the other guests and workers as the club is trying to keep up to its reputation.\r\rWhile you’re at it, find this unknown source and take him out, he should be around the area.\r\rGood luck!",
